  "title": "Crewing Officer (Shipping, Maritime) #ESY",
  "description": "<ul><li>To support the Fleet Crewing Manager in managing daily crew operations.</li><li>Help with organizing crew schedules, managing crew changes, and following up with the necessary people.</li><li>Assist in arranging travel for crew members when they join or leave their assignments (this includes booking flights, arranging visas, accommodation, etc.).</li><li>Make sure crew candidates meet all required qualifications (like medical checks and certificates).</li><li>Help out with all crew-related matters.</li><li>Do data entry, and handle recording, printing, and filing of documents.</li><li>Maintain an organized and user-friendly filing system to keep track of all department documents.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Interested candidates, please email your resume to annasee@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p></p><p>Anna See Sing Yee</p><p>CEI Reg R25157535</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 99C4599</p><p></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted</p><p></p>",
